# AI-TEXT-TO-IMAGE-GENERATOR

~Project Description

This project is a Stable Diffusion Image Generator built in Google Colab.
It uses the public model stabilityai/stable-diffusion-2-1, which requires no login or API token, making it simple to run anywhere.

~Features:

1)Generates 3 different images for any text prompt.
2)High-quality outputs with improved guidance and inference steps.
3)Works on GPU (if available) for faster generation.
4)Saves generated images as output_1.png, output_2.png, and output_3.png.
